类 Info

java.lang.Object
com.study.journey.entity.Info
public class Info extends Object
The Info class is an entity that represents information about a user in the system. It encapsulates details such as ID, class ID, name, and PIN associated with a user. There are getters and setters provided for accessing and updating these attributes. copyright : Copyright (c) 2023/5/26
